661
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:00,400
Don't move.

662
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:02,160
Or you'll die.

663
00:37:02,320 --> 00:37:04,220
Friendship Hospital is protected.

664
00:37:05,080 --> 00:37:06,200
I don't believe that.

665
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:08,120
Doctors save lives.

666
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:09,760
How can they kill people?

667
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:11,760
A surgeon's professional skill is

668
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:12,920
that even if I stab you a hundred times,

669
00:37:13,560 --> 00:37:14,600
you won't die.

670
00:37:26,600 --> 00:37:29,200
You'd better stay here forever.

671
00:37:31,100 --> 00:37:35,640
