681
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:56,680
Sakun hasn't been discharged yet.

682
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:58,840
His guardian can't be taken away.

683
00:37:58,960 --> 00:37:59,560
Boss.

684
00:38:00,120 --> 00:38:02,320
I heard you spent the night with Miss Su

685
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:04,320
