686
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:10,560
You spent the night with Dr. Gu?

687
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:11,720
No, I didn't.

688
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:13,000
He's talking nonsense.

689
00:38:20,680 --> 00:38:22,320
Hey, why are you talking nonsense here?

690
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:24,320
You're just making things up.

691
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:27,720
I'm not lying!

692
00:38:28,160 --> 00:38:30,040
The pharmacist saw you
with her own eyes.

693
00:38:30,640 --> 00:38:32,320
